        <h1 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-8">About</h1>
        <p class="mb-5 text-justify"><span class="pr-16"></span>Welcome to iBroccoGreens, a web-based parameter monitoring and misting automation with cycle level harvest tracking for Calabrese broccoli microgreens in vertical soilless farming. To access the iBroccoGreens web system, you must first agree with the terms and conditions. If you do not agree with these terms and conditions, you cannot access the iBroccoGreens web system.</p>
        <p class="mb-5 text-justify"><span class="pr-16"></span>The iBroccoGreens device is designed as an indoor vertical farming system equipped with four microgreens trays. The iBroccoGreens device integrates sensors, automation, and provides monitoring day-to-day parameters in real time such as soil moisture, soil pH, water pH, temperature and humidity to improve consistency in yield, reduce manual labor, optimize resource usage, and implement sustainable microgreens production. With automatic misting, ventilation, and lighting, the device ensures consistent growth conditions and reduces the risks of overwatering, uneven lighting, and mold contamination. The iBroccoGreens web system allows you to easily track cycle details, monitor harvest yields, and make data-driven decisions to improve productivity and efficiency. The web system also provides real-time notifications and SMS alerts to inform users when parameter conditions fall outside optimal ranges.</p>
